Alliance Trust Says Two Emerging-Market Fund Managers Left Firm

-- B y   T i m   F a r r a n d
-- 
2011-10-05T15:36:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-05/alliance-trust-says-two-emerging-market-fund-managers-left-firm.html
Alliance Trust Plc (ATST) , the U.K.’s
biggest closed-end investment fund, said two money managers in
its emerging-markets team left the company.  “I can confirm that the two roles in the emerging-markets
team have been made redundant,” a spokeswoman for the company
said by telephone today. She declined to be identified by name,
citing company policy.  John Ewart and Kevin Craig will leave with immediate
effect, she said. Ewart didn’t return a voice mail left on his
office phone at Alliance Trust in Dundee,  Scotland . Craig didn’t
immediately return a voice mail left on his mobile phone.  To contact the reporter responsible for this story
